Description: The Grove Townhomes is conveniently located in Halethorpe, Maryland and is the premier residential townhome community for individuals looking for space, style and luxury. Our two- and three-bedroom townhomes feature spacious floor plans with plenty of storage, eat-in kitchens, central air, and a private balcony or patio. Newly renovated interiors, and walk-in closets, are available in Select apartments. You will love having your own washer and dryer, as well as a private entrance. The Grove is located in a well-established residential neighborhood, and is near the renowned University of Maryland Baltimore County Campus, Catonsville Community College, and is located in Baltimore County Public Schools. Travels are made easy with nearby access to I-295 (Baltimore-Washington Parkway), I-95, and Baltimore/Washington International Airport. You will be close enough to all the excitement that Baltimore offers, yet far enough away to enjoy sunset views from your balcony or patio at The Grove Townhomes.

It has amenities like wall to wall carpeting dishwasher washer & dryer deck fenced yard 3.5 bathrooms and off street parking. Brand new carpet on the 1st and 2nd floors. Description:
(301) 703-8608 - Highland, MD - This quintessential post-modern home will make you feel at ease even in 2017! With its open floor plan and retro wood moldings in each of the three bedrooms, it has a charm that will never go out of style. One special feature that stands out the most in this home is a pink and black bathroom, a hallmark trend of the 1950~s that was started by First Lady Mamie Eisenhower~s love of pink. A must see.
(RLNE3524869) Pet policies - Small Dogs Allowed, Large Dogs Allowed.

---- SCHEDULE A SHOWING ONLINE AT: http://showmojo.com/lac/0b1c25d03a ----
Townhouse located in a quiet neighborhood just off I95 near UMBC. It has amenities such as wall to wall carpeting,dishwasher,washer & dryer,deck,fenced yard,3.5 bathrooms and off street parking. Brand new carpet on the first and second floors. The kitchen is located in the front of the house and opens to the dining/living area. Off the living area is the deck for outdoor living. A powder room is located on the main floor. The downstairs is finished to provide additional living space with a full bath.a sliding door opens onto the fenced in yard. there are two large bedrooms upstairs with large closets.The front bedroom has a private bath while the back bedroom is next to the hall bathroom. The townhouse is cable-ready. No pets. No smoking.

Description:
If you are looking for lots of space, look no further! Large 4 Bedroom 2 bathroom house located on a corner lot. The huge back/side yard is privately fenced in, and includes a fire pit and detached garage. There is an enclosed front porch that is perfect for lazy evenings, leading into the open living area and dining room. There is also a separate den/rec room. Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms, a shared full bathroom, linen closet, and attic access for storage. The finished portion of the basement features a large bedroom and another full bathroom. Washer/dryer on premises, and the heat utility is gas, saving you $$$! 
Utilities: tenant pays for electric/gas and water.
